Results.ReviewText: After some heart trouble I was forced into a life of decaffinated drinks and I scoured the supermarkets, even amazon and eBay, to find a decaffinated coffee with some sort of taste, or even just a good smell, but no luck. Eventually I gave up and went on green tea, which it's okay but not wonderful and then a couple of weeks ago a friend of mine made me a cup of decaf Nescafé Azera and I instantly panicked and thought, oh no this is real coffee! I couldn't believe it when she said it was decaf, I even made her show me the container! I've never looked back since! It's absolutely gorgeous, rich flavour and smell and it really satisfies my coffee craving. I can't recommend it enough! 10 stars!
Results.Title: The BEST tasting decaff around!
